Merry Christmas from our family to yours!!
I like me better when I’m with you 😘

Growing up one of my biggest inspirations to follow my dreams came from my uncle @davidericgomez. He had this amazing dream to dance on Broadway. He worked so hard and chased down every opportunity to reach that dream. He ended up living out his dreams and more, and one of the very first Broadway shows I saw him perform in was the @billyjoel show, Movin’ Out. Before I got to see the show, and for years after, I listened to Billy Joel on repeat learning every single song so I could sing along while I watched him in the show. He’s a dancer and I’m singer but we’re both dreamers and both Gomez’s and just like him I will never stop chasing my own dream until it comes true! Until then, enjoy one of my favorites, New York State of Mind, by @billyjoel !!❤️❤️ Thanks @thomaselees for turning this one country with me!!
